均与郑州相当。 7月19日至22日，受强降雨影响，共产主义渠合河站和卫河汲县站水位超警戒线，全市共有7座中型水库溢流，共造成辉县市、卫辉市、长垣市、获嘉县、原阳县、封丘县58个乡镇受灾。截至21日22时30分，受灾人口47万余人，农作物受灾面积5.5万余公顷，其中，成灾面积1.1万余公顷。 目前，当地组织专业抢险队伍138支、9393人，群防队伍300余支、1万余人，以及各类应急车辆、装备，开展抢险救援工作。全市已出动救灾救援力量7.6万余人次，抢险救援车辆1521辆，力争把灾害损失降到最低。（新华社）"},"attached_info":"ClQIiMHzkpC4xZYVEAMaCDY3NTk0NDI4IPK244cGMAA4TkApcgk0NzM5MTYwODB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ad96183948e52f36701d2b67498db9c7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"42_1627006910.197008","card_id":"Q_472448660","target":{"id":472448660,"title":"如果婴儿界也有奥运会，你觉得孩子可以在哪个项目上一举夺魁？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/472448660","type":"question","created":1626356711,"answer_count":55,"follower_count":97,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2265,27007,137155,160071],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClQIiMHzkpC4xZYVEAMaCDY3MjY4MDU3IOf3wIcGMAE4YUAqcgk0NzI0NDg2NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-7eeadbd3131d00cdbb12773d6c945232_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"43_1627006910.1974847","card_id":"Q_473975213","target":{"id":473975213,"title":"如何看待一些明星捐款河南被嘲「赚多捐少」？明星捐款是否可以「捐款自愿、数额自由」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/473975213","type":"question","created":1626935944,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":28,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[131,1573,8456,33529,39658],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，河南多地连续强降雨造成水灾牵动了全国，一方有难，八方支援，演艺圈的明星艺人纷纷响应捐款捐物